cs.CL, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.IR, cs.NE 

Reasoning: 
- cs.CL (Computation and Language) is the most likely category as the paper focuses on natural language processing and specifically on response selection in a dialog system. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is also likely as the paper utilizes a pre-trained language model and proposes a post-training method to improve its performance. 
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is relevant as the paper uses a deep learning model (BERT) for response selection. 
- cs.IR (Information Retrieval) is relevant as the paper focuses on retrieval-based dialog systems and response selection. 
- cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) is less likely but still possible as the paper uses a neural network model (BERT) for response selection.
